  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 400°F/ Gas 6<br /><br />Pat the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> dry with <span class=\"text-highlight\">kitchen paper</span> and season them generously on both sides with <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top and tail the <strong>butternut squash</strong> and carefully slice in half</p>\n<p>Scoop out the seeds with a spoon and discard<br /><br />Slice the <strong>butternut squash</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>red onions</strong></span> and slice into wedges</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into small, bite-sized pieces<br /><br />Chop the<strong> Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>butternut squash</strong>, <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, <strong>red onion wedges</strong> and <strong>garlic cloves</strong> (skins on) to 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> baking tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and top with the<strong> chicken thighs</strong> (skin side up)<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze over the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> then add the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>squeezed lemon</strong></span> to the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> (save the rest for later!)</p>\n<p>Roughly strip the <strong>rosemary</strong> and <strong>thyme</strong> leaves from their stems and sprinkle the leaves all over<br /><br />Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for an initial 30-35 min or until the vegetables have started to brown and soften </p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have browned, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven</p>\n<p>Remove the <strong>roasted garlic cloves</strong> and add the <strong>chopped Tenderstem broccoli</strong></p>\n<p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a further 10-15 min or until the vegetables are fork-tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic cloves</strong><br /><br />Add the <strong>chopped roasted garlic</strong> to a bowl with the juice of the remaining <strong>lemon</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\n<p>Give it a good stir – this is your <strong>roasted garlic dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2346-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken &amp; butternut tray roast </strong>with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong><br /><br />Drizzle over the<strong> roasted garlic dressing</strong> <br /><br />Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
